title: Highest and Lowest Number of Days Clear of Clouds, USA,
name: Highest and Lowest Number of Days Clear of Clouds, USA,
description: This dataset illustrates the cities with the most and least number of days clear of clouds, in US cities with 50,000 or more people.  A value of -1 means that the data was not applicable. Also included are the population, percent of days clear of  clouds, the city and state, the original city ranking, and the inverse ranking to be used only for mapping.
